{"tid":781212,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"VF將分拆Lee等牛仔褲品牌上市　集中資源發展Vans及North Face","createTime":"2018-08-15T17:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T03:53:45.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"009cf62dcbfd71aa305a447e1e05925d8600d129","tid":781212,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:04:27.000Z","msg":"大型服裝生產商VF，旗下擁有多個服裝品牌。該公司計劃分拆牛仔褲業務上市，當中包括著名牌子Lee及Wrangler等。<br />\n<br />\n公司指出，分拆牛仔褲上市，是因為要集中資源發展盈利更好的品牌，例如Vans休閒鞋和North Face戶外服裝等。<br />\n<br />\n牛仔褲曾是VF王牌　近年貢獻大不如前<br />\n<br />\n牛仔褲一度是VF的王牌產品，貢獻超過一半盈利，但隨着其他產品銷量上升，同時牛仔褲業務收入下降，重要性已經大不如前。<br />\n<br />\n該公司在美國上市，消息公布後股價下挫，收市跌3.6%。<br />\n<br />\n分拆出來的新公司，將會專注於減債及派息，另外亦會拓展中國等新興市場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/222450/vf將分拆lee等牛仔褲品牌上市-集中資源發展vans及north-face\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A%2F222450%2Fvf%E5%B0%87%E5%88%86%E6%8B%86lee%E7%AD%89%E7%89%9B%E4%BB%94%E8%A4%B2%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82-%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E6%BA%90%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95vans%E5%8F%8Anorth-face&d=IXDrlsmRLPkPJUEFbulJz%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=1cbd2279\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/222450/vf將分拆lee等牛仔褲品牌上市-集中資源發展vans及north-face</a>"},{"pid":"6050bf8e08e7ce1c0f583383af4fed9393ed3efb","tid":781212,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f72eac2a656acf47918acd397d465ecec0c49b4","tid":781212,"uid":50327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:53:45.000Z","msg":"vans 真係好好賺"}]}